import { Component, OnInit, OnDestroy } from '@angular/core'; import { Subscription } from 'rxjs'; import { SharedTableService } from 'src/app/Dev/processos/shared-tab.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-bal-extrato', templateUrl: './bal-extrato.component.html', styleUrls: ['./bal-extrato.component.css'] }) export class BalExtratoComponent implements OnInit, OnDestroy { tabelaEspelhada: any[] = []; tabelaEspelhadaSubscription: Subscription = new Subscription(); tipoEntrada: string = ''; entrada: string = ''; constructor(private sharedTableService: SharedTableService) {} ngOnInit() { this.tabelaEspelhada = this.sharedTableService.obterTabelaEspelhada(); this.tabelaEspelhadaSubscription = this.sharedTableService.tabelaEspelhadaSubject.subscribe((tabela: any[]) => { this.tabelaEspelhada = tabela; this.tabelaEspelhada = this.sharedTableService.obterTabelaOriginal(); }); } ngOnDestroy() { this.tabelaEspelhadaSubscription.unsubscribe(); } }
